    		    </script><div class="topPart clearfix tac"><h1 class="artTitle font_faus">How do currency options work?</h1></div><div class="bylineBox"><div class="dt contentwrapper"><div class="dtc vam artByline"><div class="story_title clearfix"><div class="menu_list flt"><span class="lines"><span class="line1"></span><span class="line2"></span><span class="line3"></span></span><span>SECTIONS</span></div><div class="arttitle flt">How do currency options work?</div></div>By <div class="auth"><a data-auname="Ram Sahgal - 30777" href="/etreporter/author-ram-sahgal-30777.cms" rel="author" target="_blank">Ram Sahgal</a><div class="author_box"></div></div>, <span class="ag">ET Bureau</span><span class="circle"></span><time>Last Updated: Nov 07, 2019, 06:57 PM IST</time></div><div class="dtc vam artShare flr" data-ga-action="Action"><div class="socialShare"><span class="asSprite s_icon"></span><span>Share</span><div class="share_block sharingIcon"><a class="fb shareSprite" data-dimension="1" data-ga-onshare="Facebook#Share#https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/forex/how-do-currency-options-work/articleshow/70835582.cms#/markets/forex/how-do-currency-options-work/articleshow/70835582.cms" data-share-title="How do currency options work?" data-share-url="http://www.ecoti.in/MJHyUZ8" data-src="http://www.ecoti.in/MJHyUZ8" href="javascript://" rel="nofollow"></a><a class="twt shareSprite" data-dimension="1" data-ga-onshare="Twitter#Tweet#https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/forex/how-do-currency-options-work/articleshow/70835582.cms#/markets/forex/how-do-currency-options-work/articleshow/70835582.cms" data-share-title="How do currency options work?" data-share-url="http://www.ecoti.in/uakZUb" data-src="http://www.ecoti.in/uakZUb" href="javascript://" rel="nofollow"></a><a class="in shareSprite" data-dimension="1" data-ga-onshare="LinkedIn#Share#https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/forex/how-do-currency-options-work/articleshow/70835582.cms#/markets/forex/how